\id EPH  
\h EFESUS 
\toc1 Efesus 
\toc2 Efesus 
\toc3 Efesus 
\mt1 Efesus  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Aya Pol, Negur nẽ oroya bunem, Kristus Jesus nẽ aposel wõ aun,  
\p Efesus Negur nẽ tamo kayau, Kristus Jesus el de dõ difedig anidi bun, pas enei atotof.   
\p
\v 2 Negur neda Tamada ado Odug Jesus Kristus neid wau ifenẽya ado wau inosiya, ã bun ibodõf.   
\s1 Kristus Bunem Uur Nẽ El Fiya Ifanadan  
\p
\v 3 Ada, neda Odug Jesus Kristus nẽ Tama Negur, ĩ yana talesauf, ĩ uur nẽ el fiya Kristus bun saa ilun dibodok anĩ ganan bunem el fadan.  
\v 4 Negur ĩ saa teneub ado kare fiya sã mog, ada yogon mala bun, fateul ado amuyẽ sã tabodõf nigin, Jesus bun igirnadan.  
\v 5 Wau laa fiya bun, Negur ĩ yogon wau kulĩya ado oroya kilei, Jesus Kristus bunem, ada yaleda fen, Negur nẽ gere tar wowã tauf nigin, mogo igirnadan.  
\v 6 Anĩ nigin, Negur nẽ wau ifenẽya, are Jesus Negurem ĩ nigin wau laa fedig anĩ bun, ege luwa ifanadan anĩ nẽ fula fiya medeĩya nigin, Negur yana talesauf.  
\v 7 Jesus bun, ada, yogon naud bunem kel yaleya, mosor nigin weder tu keleya anĩ, Negur nẽ wau ifenẽya barikã bunem, talen.  
\v 8 Negur ĩ yogon wau ifenẽya bunem, kisi biya ado kisi fokõya ganan, ada bun foula fen.  
\v 9 Agef fen, ĩ yogon oroya nẽ waa anĩ ifelnadan, are yogon wau kulĩya nẽ kisi Kristus bun kisi fen kilei,  
\v 10 yogon sain anĩ kisi fel wõ youf bun kabĩ yalouf, sain anĩ bun, Negur ĩ saa teneub ado bun ereb ereb ganan dibodok anĩ, mudur tekelei, Kristus farumen gurif iroulauf.   
\p
\v 11 Negur ĩ yogon oroya dõf fen, ereb ereb ganan age fedig, ĩ yogon kisi dõf fen, ada mogo igirnadan, age fe di, adag Kristus bun yogon akor talen,  
\v 12 are ada uyulil Kristus bun wauda iseya talen anĩ, Negur nẽ fula fiya medeĩya yana talesauf nigin age fen.  
\v 13 Ã momoi anĩ nẽ od, ãgenei kel yaleya nẽ biya od anĩ karĩ ge fen, ãg Kristus bun ubodõgen. Ã Kristus nigin momoi ge di, Negur ã bun uris, are Awa Uur Fateul Negur afeneĩf yen anĩ inon.  
\v 14 Negur ĩ, idi Negur nẽ anidi kel yaleya fau wõya sã mog, ada neda akor momoi bagai talouf nigin megeir fe fen, Awa Uur Fateul iben, are ada yogon fula fiya medeĩya yana talesauf nigin age fen.   
\s1 De Fiyẽya Ado Kosẽya  
\p
\v 15 Age fiya nigin, aya Odug Jesus nigin ãgenei momoiya ado, Negur nẽ tamo kayau ganan nigin ãgenei wauĩ laa fiya anĩ karĩ au fen,  
\v 16 aya ã nigin Negur de fiyẽya to folõ afelen. Aya neu kosẽya bun ã nigin karĩ aul fen,  
\v 17 neda Odug Jesus Kristus nẽ Negur, Tamada fula fiya medeĩya barikã, ĩ, ã ĩ nigin keleĩ bagai youf nigin, kisi biya ado kurõ fesiya nẽ Awa Uur ifeneĩf nigin, kosẽ audig.  
\v 18 Aya ãgenei wauĩ nẽ meleĩ fokõ fouf nigineg kosẽ audig, are ã, wau iseya ĩ anĩ bun iweignein, yogon fula fiya medeĩya barikã nẽ akor Negur nẽ tamo kayau bun ibodok anĩ ado,  
\v 19 yogon megeir barikã momoi tauf ada bun kabĩ yalef anĩ, keleĩ youf nigin, age afedig. Megeir are, yogon totol barikã anim kabĩ yalef gen,  
\v 20 megeir de tekelei anim Kristus bun kabĩ yale fen, ĩ laa bun tamal kel turĩ fiye ken, saa ilun Negur ima biyalẽ inenen.  
\v 21 Negur ĩ, Kristus, uyu irouya ganan, yeneid adodo ganan, megeir ganan, odudug ganan ado, yeneid sain enei bun ado sain fau isiyouf buneg ifenẽdiyouf ani ganan wal fiya bun inenen.  
\v 22 Agef fen, Negur ĩ, ereb ereb ganan Kristus ye farumen gõ fel fen, ĩ sios nigin ereb ereb ganan neid mudur ibodõf nigin igirnen.  
\v 23 Sios are, yogon bouwa, ĩ naab ganan bunem ereb ereb ganan kisi feledig anĩ nẽ kisi feleya.   
\c 2  
\s1 Kristus Bun Mata Tabodok  
\p
\v 1 Ã kulu ãgenei kũ fenẽya ado mosor bun gare gen.  
\v 2 Sain anĩ bun, ã teneub enei nẽ naab ado, owõbẽ tano nẽ mudur, are uur idi dõ fiya sã anidi bun gama kabĩ yalef anĩ nẽ naab dõ gen.  
\v 3 Idi atun ada gananeg, uruwa bun bouwada nẽ oroya anĩ dõ tafe fen, yogon oroya ado kisi dõ tafen. Ada, tamo tunĩ ganan idi gogũ difedin gen, adag age de gogũ difadan bunem, Negur nẽ didi farumen tabodon.  
\v 4 Anĩ ere, ada nigin yogon wau laa fiya odug bunem, Negur wau yũya barikã,  
\v 5 ĩ, ada kũ fenẽya bun gare taun sain buneg, ada Kristus geid turĩ fadan. Are wau ifenẽya bunem, ã kel yaleyein.  
\v 6 Agef fen, Negur ĩ, ada Kristus geid kel turĩ fada fen, Kristus Jesus bun ada ĩ geid saa ilun tabodõf nigin inenadan,  
\v 7 are, fau isiyouf sain bun, ĩ yogon biya fiya Kristus Jesus bun ifanadan anĩ bunem, yogon wau ifenẽya barikã ifelnẽdiyouf nigin age fen.  
\v 8 Wau ifenẽya bunem, ã momoiya bunem kel yaleyein, are aug bunem sã, Negur nẽ ege luwa ifenein,  
\v 9 are kabĩ bunem sã, anĩ nigin, taka nem to yana yalesauf.  
\v 10 Ada Negur nẽ imaba, kabĩ biya talouf nigin Kristus Jesus bun ada kare fadan, kabĩ biya are Negur ada age tafouf nigin uruwa bun mogo dodok fanadan.   
\s1 Kristus Bun Ada Tekelei  
\p
\v 11 Anĩ nigin, uruwa bun, ã gõ diyein bunem haiden ubodõge di, idi mulũ dilen anidim (are tamo bouwa bun tamo imedim age difen) ã mulũ ileya sã diyein anĩ karĩ weleg.  
\v 12 Sain anĩ bun, ã Kristus nigin gerõ ufaregen, ã Israel buneg yeneĩ sã, promis nẽ bar itenẽya buneg ã yaũ, tenebur ein wau iseya sã, Negur nigin keleĩ sã ubodõgen anĩ karĩ weleg.  
\v 13 Anĩ ere, gama ã uruwa gerõ ufaregen anĩ, Kristus Jesus bun, Kristus nẽ naud bunem, Negur non guri yeĩ irousiyein.   
\p
\v 14 Ere nigin, Kristus yogo ĩ neda maror, uru anĩ yale, tekelei inon, agef fen, kiwai fara fiya nẽ garaĩ anĩ narĩ fen.  
\v 15 Ĩ yogo bouwa bunem lo, ĩtãfiya ado, nun anĩ yaleledin. Ĩ yogo bun tamo uru anĩ bunem, tamo mata tekelei ino fen, maror inouf nigin age fen.  
\v 16 Ĩ bouwa tekelei enei bun, idi uruwom aa tetek bunem Negur bun komo fediyouf nigin agef fen, ĩ aa tetek bunem dogo neid kiwai yukesin.  
\v 17 Ĩ isi fen, ã haiden gerõ ufaregen bun maror nigin wogõ yei ken, idi Juda temeleid non difaren anidi buneg, maror nigin wogõ fiyẽdin.  
\v 18 Ĩ bunem, ada uruwom Awa Uur tekelei bunem, Tamada wagen ileya kisi feleya.   
\p
\v 19 Anĩ nigin, ã yaũ tamo ado tamo urug sã, anĩ ere, Negur nẽ tamo kayau geid tekelei fen, Negur nẽ ibor tar.  
\v 20 Ã, aposel ado profet fõ gariya dinon anĩ teten fõ gen inoyein, are Kristus Jesus yogo ĩ monog tor gen.  
\v 21 Kristus bun, fõ ganan katõ fel fen, Odug bun tempel fateul wõ youf nigin fã yef.  
\v 22 Kristus bun, ãg, mata ibodõya nẽ modoũ Negur yogon Awa Uur bunem ibodõf nẽ anĩ wõ gouf nigin, weim inoyeik.   
\c 3  
\s1 Pol Haiden Bun Biya Od Wogõya Tamo  
\p
\v 1 Age fiya nigin, aya Pol, haiden ã nigin, Kristus Jesus nẽ kabĩ nigin au fen, kalabus bun abodok.   
\p
\v 2 Momoi bagai, Negur nẽ wau ifenẽya ã nigin aya ifanan anĩ, naig fe kabĩ yalen are, ã karĩ gen.  
\v 3 Are waa Negurem kurõ fesiya bunem aya ifelnan, are aya mogo tobega bagai atoton gen.  
\v 4 Ã enei uweseg fen, Kristus nẽ waa nigin aya wederou fokõ felen anĩ, keleĩ youf.  
\v 5 Are Awa Uurem Negur nẽ fateul aposel ado profet bun gama kurõ fesin gen, sain mogo ilelen anĩ nẽ tamo kayau bun tamo idi to agef ifelnẽdin.  
\v 6 Waa are, biya od bunem, haiden idi Israel geid Negur nẽ akor dalouf, idi ganan bouwa tekelei nẽ bagu fiya dibodõf, agef fen, Kristus Jesus bun promis nẽ akor anĩ weim dalouf.   
\p
\v 7 Negur nẽ megeir kabĩ yale di, aya Negur nẽ wau ifenẽya ege luwa ifanan anĩ bunem, biya od enei nẽ kabĩ tamo wõ aun.  
\v 8 Negur nẽ tamo kayau ganan atun, tamo naal farumen aya gai naal bagai anĩ, wau ifenẽya enei aya ifanan, are Kristus nẽ kisi feleya, are imir ken, ileya kisi feleya sã anĩ, haiden bun wogõ auf nigin ado,  
\v 9 waa enei, kulu isin ganan Negur ereb ereb ganan kare fen anĩ bun iminẽyan ibodon anĩ, naig fe kabĩ yalef anĩ, tamo kayau ganan bun yaor afouf nigin ifanan.  
\v 10 Negur nẽ kisi are, gama sios bunem, Negur nẽ kisi biya fire fire, saa ilun uyu iroudiya ado yeneid adodo ifelnẽdiyouf,  
\v 11 are Negur ĩ, yogon mata ibodkeleya nẽ oroya, neda Odug Kristus Jesus bun kisif bure felen anĩ kilei, age fen.  
\v 12 Kristus bun, ada Kristus nigin momoiya bunem, karika ado kumĩ sã, Negur wagen ileya kisi feleya.  
\v 13 Anĩ nigin, aya ã arokeneik, aya ã nigin darau alef ge fen, to felu gouf, darau are ã fula fiya medeĩya ifeneĩya nigin.   
\s1 Efesus Sios Nigin Kosẽya  
\p
\v 14 Gariya enei nigin, Dei ĩ bunem, yogon ibor ganan saa ilun ado tenebur ein dibodok,  
\v 15 dogo neid yeneid yaledig, aya ĩ wagen iborou bobou afef.  
\v 16 Aya kosẽ auf, ĩ yogon fula fiya medeĩya kisi feleya bunem, yogon Awa Uur bunem megeir ã namein ife fen, megeir yeĩf nigin,  
\v 17 are Kristus ĩ momoiya bunem ãgenei wauĩ bun ibodõf nigin. Age afe fen, aya kosẽ auf, ã warumutei ado gariya, wau laa fiya bun utenẽg fen,  
\v 18 ã Negur nẽ tamo kayau ganan geid, Kristus nẽ wau laa fiya anĩ, odug naig be fiya, meluk, ilun ado, namen naig be fiya anĩ ulogouf nigin megeir walogouf,  
\v 19 agog fen, wau laa fiya enei, keleĩ ganan wal fiya anĩ keleĩ youf, anĩ bunem, Negur nẽ kisi feleya ganan ã bun kisi falauf nigin kosẽ auf.   
\p
\v 20 Ĩ gama yogon megeir ada namedan kabĩ yalef anĩ bunem, ereb ada to tafef be, kisi tafef anĩ ganan wal fiya, age fiya kisi feleya,  
\v 21 sios bun ado Kristus Jesus bun, fula fiya medeĩya, ibor ganan gai gai ibodok ilauf bun, ĩ bun ibodõf! Momoi.   
\c 4  
\s1 Kristus Bouwa Bun Bagu Fiya  
\p
\v 1 Aya Kristus nigin kalabus bun abod ken, iweigya ã walegen kilei, mata ubodõgouf nigin totol bagai arokeneik.  
\v 2 Ã wauĩ adok ukalaisileg fen, molol bagai ubodõgouf. Ã to feseg, wauĩ laa fiya bun abob nẽ morõ uteĩgouf.  
\v 3 Awa Uur maror bunem bagu yein anĩ uroug kafĩ walagauf nigin, kabĩ totol waleg.  
\v 4 Sain ã iweignein, ã wau iseya tekelei bun iweignein, age fiya gen, bouwa tekelei, Awa Uur tekelei,  
\v 5 Odug tekelei, momoiya tekelei, naan igũya tekelei,  
\v 6 Negur tekelei, ĩ ganan neid Temeid, ĩ ganan wal fiya, ĩ ganan atun, ĩ ganan namen ibodok.   
\p
\v 7 Anĩ ere, ada mugu mugu wau ifenẽya, Kristus ege luwa ifenẽya nigin kisi fen kilei, ifanadan.  
\v 8 Negur nẽ Itotoya anĩ nigin eig ye irok,  
\q1 “Ĩ ilun iselen sain,  
\q2 ĩ tamo musei geif irou iselen,  
\q2 agef fen, ĩ tamo ege luwa ifenẽdin.”\f + \fr 4:8  \ft Sam 68:18\f*   
\m
\v 9 (“Ĩ ilun iselen” ya nẽ gariya are ere? Anĩ nẽ gariya are, ĩ tenebur farumen bagai buneg isilen.  
\v 10 Ĩ isilen are, ĩ anĩ saa ilun ganan wal fiya iselen, are owõ ganan inolauf nigin age fen.)  
\v 11 Inim anĩ, tunĩ aposel kabĩ, tunĩ profet kabĩ, tunĩ soosi kabĩ, tunĩ pastor kabĩ ado tise kabĩ ifenẽdin,  
\v 12 are Negur nẽ tamo kayau, aruna yaleya kabĩ dalouf nigin dodok fedi di, Kristus nẽ bouwa odugouf nigin age fen.  
\v 13 Agef ile ile, ada ganan, momoiya tekelei ado Negur Naal nigin keleĩ tekelei bun tasi fen, tamo kisi feleya bagai wõ tau fen, Kristus nẽ kisi feleya bagai bun talauf.   
\p
\v 14 Age tafouf, ada baban momou gen to tabodõf, maaĩ moloun wĩya gen to age ta fen, tai fiya ganan, tamo neid beugya ado, idegẽya tamo neid kisi anidim, yaum fũ fe di, aarau ilef isif fedig gen, to wewu fadauf.  
\v 15 Age fiya ban, ada wau laa fiya bun momoi anĩ wogõ tau fen, ereb ereb ganan bun Mudur ibodok bun biya daf iselauf, Mudur are Kristus.  
\v 16 Ĩ bunem, dirumunã ganan bouwa isenne ken, katokitĩ fe, bagu fele di, bouwa nẽ fara fiya mugu mugu yogon kabĩ yalef bunem, bouwa adok odug fen, wau laa fiya bun yogo inof.   
\s1 Lalan Nẽ Gere Tar Gen Tabodõf  
\p
\v 17 Anĩ nigin, aya enei Odug bun totol bagai arokeneik, ã baban, haiden idi difaredig gen, kisi sã gen to ufaragauf.  
\v 18 Idi neid kisi gugum kel fen, Negur nẽ mata bun ibodõya ditoron, ere nigin, idi wedereid to fokõ ye fen, waud totolen.  
\v 19 Idi es fiya kisi ganan ditor ken, idi dogo bouweid adok sane bun difen ken, ereb ereb sane ganan, dogo nigin dogol, es fiya sã age difedig.   
\p
\v 20 Anĩ ere, ã Kristus nigin naab anĩ bunem to kelein.  
\v 21 Momoi bagai, ã ĩ nigin karĩ gen ado, ĩ bun difelnein, are momoi Jesus bun ibodok anĩ kilei.  
\v 22 Ã uruwa ubodõgen, ãgenei oroya tubu, yogon idegẽya oroya bunem sane len anĩ, utorõg fen,  
\v 23 ãgenei kisi nẽ tobonunã bun mata wõg fen,  
\v 24 oroya mata, madur bagai ado momoi nẽ fateul bun Negur gen inon anĩ, ufonũgouf nigin difelnein.   
\p
\v 25 Anĩ nigin, ã mugu mugu idegẽya utorõg fen, ã neĩ tã momoi nem urokenẽgouf, ere nigin, ada ganan bouwa tekelei nẽ tunĩ.  
\v 26 “Ãgenei seyeya bun, mosor to unog.”\f + \fr 4:26  \ft Sam 4:4\f* Ã wauĩ bun to seye yef ile, gaa kuru kalauf.  
\v 27 Agog fen, ã Satan nẽ modoũ taka to utoumkenẽgouf.  
\v 28 Aib ĩ bẽ ilenouf, baban to bẽ ilauf, anĩ ere, yogo imam ereb biya nigin kabĩ yale di, ĩ lau difef anidi ifenẽdiya nigin safina adouf.   
\p
\v 29 Ãgenei eweĩ bun od sesen to wõ youf, anĩ ere, idi lau difef anidi fã de dalouf nigin isennẽya od anĩ dogol urõge di, idi karĩ def are isennẽdiyouf.  
\v 30 Negur nẽ Awa Uur Fateul to wau morõ wenẽg, ĩ bunem kel yaleya nẽ naa nigin uris ã bun inon.  
\v 31 Ereb ereb dirikeĩ ganan, didi fatuk iseya, seyeya, gurũya, dumen od irõya ado, ereb ereb sane ganan utorõg.  
\v 32 Abob el wiyẽg fen, abob nigin wauĩ yu ken, Negur ĩ Kristus bun ãgenei mosor nigin weder tu kelen gen, abob nẽ mosor nigin wedereĩ tu kalauf.   
\c 5  
\p
\v 1 Anĩ nigin, ã Negur gere tar oboi nigin, ĩ gen bagai ago gouf.  
\v 2 Kristus ada nigin wau laaf fen, ada nigin yogo bouwa ofa ado sesewi fiya sumeĩ biya gen Negur ifenen gen, wauĩ laa fiya bun agog ubodõgouf.   
\p
\v 3 Anĩ ere, ã atun, naal bagai noli tobonunã be, ereb amuyẽ ado taka be, safina musei youf nigin ima su lai fe fen sũ we fiya taka to ibodõf, ere nigin, eneidi are Negur nẽ fateul tamo kayau bun to biya.  
\v 4 Takag, od sesen, neneya od be, od sane nem weli to unogouf, are ada nigin to biya, anĩ ere, de fiyẽya od wogõ gouf.  
\v 5 Ere nigin, ã momoi bagai enei keleĩ: Tamo noli tobonunã ado, amuyẽ ado be, safina musei youf nigin ima su lai fe fen sũ we fiya (tamo age fiya are idegẽya waitou yana yaleseya tamo), ĩ Kristus ado Negur nẽ tano bun akor to yalouf.  
\v 6 To lo ge di, taka nem od egem idegneĩf, ere nigin, age fediya bunem Negur nẽ didi, idi nokũ difef anidi bun isidig.  
\v 7 Anĩ nigin, idi geid to nigal ũgouf.   
\p
\v 8 Ere nigin, ã uruwa bun gugum, anĩ ere, gama Odug bun ã lalan. Lalan nẽ gere tar gen agog ufareg.  
\v 9 Ere nigin, lalan nẽ faat are, biya fiya, madur bagai ado, momoi anĩ ganan bun ibodok.  
\v 10 Agog fen, ereb Odug wau al fouf anĩ keleĩ youf.  
\v 11 Ereb gugum bun tamal tobonunã faat biya sã anĩ geid to nigal ũgouf, anĩ ere, yaor wedigouf.  
\v 12 Ere nigin, ereb fe temeleid iminẽyan age difedig anĩ nigin irõya, areg mama ado.  
\v 13 Anĩ ere, ereb ereb ganan lalan bun yaor fef, are yaoredig,  
\v 14 ere nigin, lalan anim age fe di, ereb ereb ganan yaoredig. Enei nigin wogõya eig yef,  
\q1 “Fã wale, mulaĩ tamal,  
\q2 laa bun tamal fã wo,  
\q1 ago di, Kristus õ bun fula fouf.”\f + \fr 5:14  \ft Asaia 26:19; 60:1; Rom 13:11\f*   
\p
\v 15 Anĩ nigin, ãgenei ibodõya nigin el ge lo walagauf. Kisi sã gen to ufaragauf, anĩ ere, kisi biya ado gen ufaragauf.  
\v 16 Naa biya ã nigin wõ youf ganan to sekil gouf, ere nigin, naa are sane.  
\v 17 Anĩ nigin, to neneg, anĩ ere, Odug nẽ oroya naig fiya anĩ ã keleĩ youf.  
\v 18 Ã wain musei to wõ ge di, meleĩ waĩ youf, are bouwa nẽ oroya nigin totol sane wau fãya bun irouleyeĩf. Age fiya ban, Awa Uurem nameĩ isokosauf.  
\v 19 Od Negur nẽ Itotoya Sam bun ibodok, Negur yana yaleseya seg ado, uur nẽ seg bunem abob wogõ wiyẽgouf. Ãgenei wauĩ bun Odug bun seg waleg fen, kakũ gouf.  
\v 20 Sain ganan bun, Negur Tamada ereb ereb ganan nigin, neda Odug Jesus Kristus yana bun de wiyẽgouf.   
\p
\v 21 Kristus anini wiyẽg fen, abob farumen ubodõg.   
\s1 Tamo Aiwa Ado Kayau Aiwa  
\p
\v 22 Kayau, ã Odug farumen ubodõgedig gen, aiweĩ tar farumen ubodõgouf.  
\v 23 Ere nigin, Kristus ĩ, sios nẽ mudur ibodok gen, tamo ĩ kayau nẽ mudur ibodok, agef fen, Kristus ĩ sios, yogon bouwa nẽ kel yaleya tamo.  
\v 24 Sios Kristus farumen ibodok gen, kayau idig ereb ereb ganan bun, dogo neid aiweid tar farumen dibodõf.   
\p
\v 25 Tamo, Kristus sios nigin wau laaf fen, yogo bouwa ĩ nigin ifenen gen, aiweĩ tar nigin wauĩ laa fouf.  
\v 26 Kristus ĩ anĩ age fen, are sios fateul ibodõf nigin od bunem naan nem fili youf nigin kulof fen,  
\v 27 are sios medeĩya bagai, diri sã, ifokoĩya be, ereb age fiya taka sã, anĩ ere, fateul fen bouwa od sã, yogo bun iroulauf nigin age fen.  
\v 28 Age fiya bagai, tamo dogo bouweid nigin waud laa fedig gen, aiweid tar nigin agef waud laa fouf. Aib ĩ aiwa nigin wau laa fef, are yogo nigin wau laa fef.  
\v 29 Aibem taka yogo bouwa to sane fiyẽdig, anĩ ere, ĩ ifout ken, kulatun fedig, Kristus sios nigin age fedig gen,  
\v 30 ere nigin, ada yogon bouwa nẽ tunĩ.  
\v 31 Are Negur nẽ Itotoya eig ye irok kilei, “Age fiya nigin, tamo ĩ yogon tama sina ado itorneĩd fen, yogon aiwa ado bagu difouf, age de fen, idi uruwom bouweid tekelei youf.”\f + \fr 5:31  \ft Jenesis 2:24\f*  
\v 32 Waa enei are, odug bagai, anĩ ere, aya Kristus ado sios nigin wogõ auf.  
\v 33 Anĩ ere, ã aug nigin wauĩ laa fedig gen, ã mugu mugu ãgenei kayau tar nigineg agog wauĩ laa fouf. Age fe di, kayau ĩ yogon tamo farumen ibodõf.   
\c 6  
\s1 Sina Tama Kesu Tar Geid  
\p
\v 1 Kesu, Odug bun sineĩ temeĩ tar sigoreid dõ gouf, ere nigin, anĩ madur.  
\v 2 “Sinã tamã yeneid walesauf,” are ĩtãfiya matu promis ado bagu fen,  
\v 3 “anĩ bunem, õ ibodõya biya ile di, tenebur ein sain meluk ubodõf.”\f + \fr 6:3  \ft Eksodas 20:12; Diuteronomi 5:16\f*  
\v 4 Tama tar, gereneĩ tar waud saneya to wenẽdig, age fiya ban, Odug nẽ tai fiya ado ifelnẽya bunem lo wedigouf.   
\s1 Ferfer Ado Marau Tamo  
\p
\v 5 Ferfer, ã Kristus dõ gounẽ gen, tenebur ein ãgenei marau tamo, kumĩ ado aniniya ado, wauĩ adok bunem sigoreid dõ gouf.  
\v 6 Ã meleid yaleya bunem to sigoreid dõ gouf, anĩ ere, Kristus nẽ ferfer gen, Negur nẽ oroya, ãgenei wauĩ adok bunem ago gouf.  
\v 7 Ã Odug aruna walogounẽ gen, tamo nigin sã, wauĩ adok yen ken, aruneid walogouf,  
\v 8 ere nigin, ã keleĩ, ĩ ferfer be, kafĩ fiya sã, Odug ĩ mugu mugu ganan, ereb biya age difef anĩ kilei, mala solo ifenẽdiyouf.   
\p
\v 9 Marau tamo ã, ãgenei ferfer naab de anĩ bunem el wedigouf. To kumĩya wenẽdig, ere nigin, ã keleĩ, ã ado idi nigin, ãgenei Marau saa ilun ibodok, ĩ bun taka nigin dogol anĩ, kinau ya sã.   
\s1 Negur Nẽ Kusĩ Nẽ Saki  
\p
\v 10 Od idĩya nigin, Odug bun ado yogon megeir barikã bun, totol ufareg.  
\v 11 Negur nẽ kusĩ nẽ saki ganan waleg, naki weleg fen, Satan nẽ kisi, fe fiyẽya nigin, sã megeir ufaragauf.  
\v 12 Ere nigin, ada neda kusĩ are, bouwa ado naud nẽ oroya fe fiyẽya nigin sã, anĩ ere, uyu iroudiya, yeneid adodo, tenebur nẽ gugum nẽ megeir ado, saa ilun kaa sesen nẽ megeir nẽ totol fe fiyẽya nigin.  
\v 13 Anĩ nigin, Negur nẽ kusĩ nẽ saki ganan waleg, naki weleg, anĩ bunem, sesen nẽ naa wõ ye di, ã tutub yũ ifareya nigin kisi feleya, agog fen, ã ereb ereb ganan agog fen, ufaragauf.  
\v 14 Anĩ nigin, totol ufareg, momoi nẽ lũ luweĩ gug fen, madur bagai nẽ siot kapam akoreĩ dedeg,  
\v 15 agog fen, ãgenei yeĩ bun su ufonũg fen, maror nẽ biya od wogõya nigin dodok fiya saika ufaragauf.  
\v 16 Enei ganan bun tobol fe fen, momoiya nẽ makanam waleg, anĩ bunem, ã sesen nẽ magir yã bale ado isif anĩ ganan, sã gare walagauf.  
\v 17 Agog fen, kel yaleya nẽ hat kapa ado Awa Uur nẽ dimig, are Negur nẽ od, anĩ waleg. \fig Negur nẽ kusĩ nẽ saki.|src="hk00194c.tif" size="span" ref="6:11-17" \fig*  
\v 18 Kosẽya ado to fiya ganan bun, sain ganan Awa Uur bun kosẽ gouf. Enei kisi bun unog fen, saika ge fen, sain ganan Negur nẽ tamo kayau ganan nigin kosẽ gouf.   
\p
\v 19 Aya nigineg kosẽ gouf, are sain aya od arõf bun ganan, Negurem od ifana fen, aya kumĩ sã biya od nẽ waa anĩ wogõ auf nigin ago gouf.  
\v 20 Biya od enei nigin, aya soosi tamo wõ au fen, kalabus bun abodok. Aya to kumĩ au fen, biya od sã kurõ afalaisiyouf nigin kosẽg.   
\s1 Idikeleya Nẽ Aanya  
\p
\v 21 Tikikus, turau oboiyou fen Odug bun kabĩ tamo dõ fiya biya, ĩ ereb ereb ganan irokeneĩf, age fe di, ãg, aya naig be afef ado aya ere kabĩ alef anĩ, keleĩ youf.  
\v 22 Aya, ĩ, gariya enei nigin bagai ã gein sur afef, are ã amã naig be fiya mabodok anĩ keleĩ youf nigin ado, ĩ ãgenei wauĩ megeir fouf nigin.   
\p
\v 23 Tamada Negur ado Odug Jesus Kristus bunem, turau tar, wau inosiya ã bun ibodõf, agef fen, wau laa fiya momoiya ado ã bun isiyouf.  
\v 24 Idi, neda Odug Jesus Kristus nigin waud laaf fen, waud laa fiya anĩ to folõ difeledig anidi ganan bun, wau ifenẽya ibodõf.   